# React UI

Visual design: [docs/UI-DESIGN.md](../../docs/UI-DESIGN.md) · Cursor rule: `ui-design.mdc`

## Page Inventory (MVP)

Welcome → Upload → **Generating** (single loading state) → **Result** → Naming → Desktop pet + panels (chat, pomodoro, growth, settings, pet manager).

Deferred to later versions (keep in roadmap, not deleted): **style pick page**, pose picker.
Removed from MVP flow: image processing/editor page.

## User-Facing Creation (3 steps)

1. Upload image
2. Wait (show progress, not pipeline steps)
3. Use pet (from result page)

## Onboarding Copy

- Title: `上传一张照片，让它住进你的电脑。`
- Primary CTA: `创建我的桌宠`
- Secondary: `先体验示例宠物`

## Result Page

Display final generated pet PNG only.

| Button | Action |
|--------|--------|
| Use This Pet | Confirm → naming → desktop |
| Regenerate | Re-run MiniMax + rembg |
| Upload Another Photo | Back to upload |

Never show rembg step, original cutout, or edit tools.

## Generating Page

- Single indeterminate or staged loader ("Creating your pet…")
- Do not expose MiniMax/rembg as separate user steps

## Component Guidelines

- Functional components + hooks
- Tailwind for layout
- Use `components/ui/`: `Button`, `TextButton`, `LinkButton`, `Pill`, `SegmentedControl`, `Toggle`, `StyleCard`, `PanelHeader`, `Input`, `PageShell` — no ad-hoc button styles
- Panel headers: `PanelHeader` with `onClose` for 关闭
- Single-select chips: `Pill` (性格、尺寸、姿势)
- Bubble: 5s auto-hide, hover pauses, single instance, reminders > chat
- Error states per failure type (upload / generation / rembg) with correct CTAs

## Pet Personality (naming step)

`温柔陪伴型` | `元气鼓励型` | `傲娇吐槽型` | `安静治愈型` | `严格监督型`

## UX Targets

- First pet < 1 minute end-to-end
- Warm companion tone; zero image-editing complexity
